IN RE SOUTHEASTERN EYE CENTER-PENDING MATTERS In re Southeastern Eye Center-Judgments No. 358A16 Supreme Court of North Carolina. March 1, 2018

ORDER

Morgan, J.

Appellants have failed to demonstrate grounds for appellate review under N.C.G.S. 7A-27(a)(3) (2017). The appeals in this matter are therefore dismissed.
